<div class="row">
  <div class="col-12">
    <%= link_to "Back to All Demos", root_path %>
    <h1>Motion Demos - Clock</h1>
    <p>A pure-Ruby implementation of a clock face.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>No JS is used to execute this, only CSS and Ruby</li>
      <li>The page is never reloaded</li>
      <li>No frontend model/store/reducer required.  The server broadcasts changes to time.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <section class="my-4 col-md-8 col-sm-12">
    <%= render ClockComponent.new %>
  </section>
</div>
